sf_detectorTemplate: Network errors exceed % based on activity
sf_description:
Alerts at various severity levels as the % of network errors based on packet activity increases past meaningful thresholds
Critical - 20% errors
Major - 15% errors
Minor - 10% errors
Warning - 5% errors
